T1  - Trainees' Attributes and Attitudes: Neglected Influences on Training Effectiveness
AU  - Noe, Raymond A.
Y1  - 1986/10/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1986.4283922
