T1  - Developing a Process Model of Problem Recognition
AU  - Cowan, David A.
Y1  - 1986/10/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1986.4283930
DO  - 10.5465/amr.1986.4283930
